dc_title_s: Davis County, Iowa, 1969, aerial photomosaic index
dc_description_s: Title supplied by cataloger based on information from sheet labels. Images are photoreductions of mosaics created from original aerial photographs. Designating symbol AJB. Form of individual image numbering: AJB-1KK-[number], or AJB-2KK-[number]. Year Flown 1969. Flown by Park Aerial Surveys, Inc. Louisville, K.Y. Approximate scale, 1:20,000|Contact the Map Collection at The University of Iowa Libraries: http://www.lib.uiowa.edu/maps/contact/|Scanned at 300 ppi in Greyscale.
